🔷 6. Key Points for Exams

✔ All requests start from public/index.php
✔ Middleware filters requests
✔ Routes decide controller
✔ Controller handles logic
✔ Model interacts with database
✔ View returns output

🔥 7. Importance of Request Lifecycle

✔ Helps understand Laravel architecture
✔ Important for debugging
✔ Used in interviews
✔ Core concept of MVC frameworks

⭐ Final Short Summary

👉 Laravel Request Lifecycle is the flow of a request from browser → index.php → middleware → route → controller → model → view → response → browser.
